| `fundingAmount`  | Decimal |      Yes |             |
| `user_id`        | Integer |      Yes |             |

#### Example

```
{
  "tripName": "Test project 1",
  "tripType": "Tech",
  "description": "Small tech business test project 1",
  "fundingAmount": 5000.00,
  "user_id": 1, 
